column8: Partly cloudy. The chance of early fog. Slight (30%) chance of a shower this morning. Light winds.
Partly cloudy. Winds southerly 15 to 20 km/h tending west to northwesterly in the middle of the day then tending east to southeasterly in the evening.
Mostly sunny. Winds east to northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h turning north to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.

Partly cloudy. Slight (30%) chance of a shower in the morning and afternoon. Winds north to northwesterly 20 to 30 km/h tending west to northwesterly 15 to 25 km/h during the day then shifting southerly 15 to 20 km/h during the evening.
Partly cloudy. Medium (50%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm later in the day. Winds northeasterly 15 to 20 km/h tending northwest to northeasterly 15 to 25 km/h during the morning.
Cloudy. Very high (95%) chance of showers. The chance of a thunderstorm. Winds northerly 30 to 45 km/h.

Partly cloudy. Very high (90%) chance of showers or snow, most likely during the morning. The chance of a thunderstorm during the morning. Winds northwesterly 25 to 30 km/h shifting south to southwesterly 20 to 30 km/h during the morning.
